	<div tal:condition="is_admin" class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-2"></div>
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<h1><span class="font-semi-bold">Special rights</span></h1>
				<p>Only the administrator has some special rights and this is the placeholder.
					<br>
					<input id="" type="button" name="" value="Get a database dump" class="button button-block btn-xs btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal" />
					<input id="list-all-users" type="button" name="" value="List all users" class="button button-block btn-xs btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal" />	

				<div id="admins-space"> </div>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-2"></div>
		</div>
